OL,3,CEmergency staff aiming for Guinness
OL,4,CWorld Record in online CPR lessons
OL,6,FEmergency staff are attempting a
OL,7,FGuinness World Record in online CPR
OL,8,Flessons in Hawick.
OL,10,FSave a Life Scotland are organising
OL,11,Fthe event to encourage as many people
OL,12,Fas possible to learn CPR in line with
OL,13,FScotland's Out of Hospital Cardiac
OL,14,FArrests strategy.
OL,16,FThe livestream of CPR lessons on
OL,17,FYoutube needs up to 1500 viewers in
OL,18,Forder to set a new record.
