OL,4,CWorld Record in online CPR lessons
OL,6,FWith the chance of survival dropping
OL,7,Fby 10% for every minute CPR is not
OL,8,Fperformed, Lee's twin brother Liam
OL,9,FMyers, a police officer, says people
OL,10,Flearning CPR will help patients
OL,11,Freceive quicker help.
OL,13,FHe said: "Ultimately this training is
OL,14,Fto save lives in the community. The
OL,15,Fmore people that are trained in CPR,
OL,16,Fthe quicker we can get help to
OL,17,Fsomebody and that will save a life."
OL,19,FThe livestream CPR training event is
OL,20,Falso being held ahead of World Restart
OL,21,FA Heart Day on 16 October 2024.
